  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK665">
<l>vīṟeyti māṇṭār viṉaittiṭpam vēntaṉka </l>
<l>ṇūṟeyti yuḷḷap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The firmness in action of those who have become great by the excellence (of their counsel) will, by attaining its fulfilment in the person of the king, be esteemed (by all).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
